#Release notes 28.04.2017:
- Company Comparison Option Added: A 'compare' button has been added to your inbox within Corporate Messenger. Any change detected outside of NowInfinity will be displayed as a 'change detected' notfication. Once you click the 'compare' button you will see a old and new profile opn which highlights the changes in yellow.
- Standard Company and Special Purpose Company Update: A 'made a mistake' section has been added to the collboration page with Form 492 available. Now when you click on 'create 492 form' you will be redirected to the pre-filled 492 form.
- For Admins only: On the completed document page there is now an option to 're-merge document'. This worked for signed documents only. Use this option is a Deed of Ratification was not created for the Trust for any particular reason. Also, bundle re-merge is now available.
- A 'delete' button has been added for any ASIC documents with a 'rejected' status on the collaboration page.
- There is now a 'check debt' button available within the debt section of company profiles.
